{"tid":653721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泛民遊行促釋放劉霞","createTime":"2018-05-05T03:44:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-05T04:33:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"47df38e1f54e9154594bd12a3888b5df4b736439","tid":653721,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T03:44:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180505/20381930?_ga=2.79173140.1018314744.1525409067-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180505%2F20381930%3F_ga%3D2.79173140.1018314744.1525409067-1555213041.1517019171&d=XjwNfyPmt1PsQncB7d9s%2FcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=1e51acc7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180505%2F20381930%3F_ga%3D2.79173140.1018314744.1525409067-1555213041.1517019171&h=443f37c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180505/20381930?_ga=2.79173140.1018314744.1525409067-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n泛民遊行促釋放劉霞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180505/large/05la5p17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180505%2Flarge%2F05la5p17.jpg&h=1be40a4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】已故諾貝爾和平獎得主劉曉波的遺孀劉霞（圖），在劉曉波死後一直被中共軟禁，在近日曝光劉霞的電話錄音中，披露劉霞有以死抗爭的想法，情況令人關注。多個泛民政黨昨早遊行至中聯辦，促中共釋放劉霞，停止政治迫害。<br />\n<br />\n支聯會主席何俊仁、社民連前立法會議員梁國雄、民主黨主席胡志偉、公民黨議員郭家麒等十多名民主派人士，持橫額高叫「釋放劉霞」口號，遊行至中聯辦。郭家麒批評中共「蝦女人」軟禁劉霞，非常可恥，指劉霞因丈夫劉曉波獲諾貝爾和平獎而被軟禁是無辜，促當局還劉霞自由，讓她出國就醫。<br />\n<br />\n胡志偉指中共禁錮劉霞，違憲法保障國民人身自由的規定，「大國崛起，都仍然打壓劉霞人身自由，呢個係咩嘅國度？」他呼籲中共還劉霞自由，還民運人士自由。何俊仁亦對事件感震怒，轟中共無法無天，到了瘋狂鎮壓人民的地步。何呼籲世界各地華人到領事館抗議，要求中共釋放異見人士。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳嘉裕  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n洗刷國殤之柱　無港大學生代表<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n《爆相爆片》四月第四輪揭曉"},{"pid":"ccdc3fad65e58cdbeff4775f8508fa96fda510de","tid":653721,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T04:30:02.000Z","msg":"又做show搵錢"},{"pid":"4adfcc0ba821e38ffa65b7928a53e877173eac5f","tid":653721,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T04:30:37.000Z","msg":"泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/123036_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F123036_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=8acef317&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13b41122a207c99195fa9b2a02efa60b7da738e0","tid":653721,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccdc3fad65e58cdbeff4775f8508fa96fda510de","tid":653721,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T04:30:02.000Z","msg":"又做show搵錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T04:33:51.000Z","msg":"以前唔會咁諗，而家真係咁諗<br />\n劉曉波死咁耐，劉霞軟禁咁耐，泛冇出過聲<br />\n岩岩宣佈和平獎會永遠等假劉霞黎拎，轉頭遊行要求釋放劉霞<br />\n超級做 show 感覺"}]}